<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sprig</title>
  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans';
      src: url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Regular.woff') format('woff'),
        url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Regular.woff2') format('woff2');
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans';
      src: url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Italic.woff') format('woff'),
        url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Italic.woff2') format('woff2');
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans';
      src: url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Bold.woff') format('woff'),
        url('https://assets.hackclub.com/fonts/Phantom_Sans_0.7/Bold.woff2') format('woff2');
      font-weight: bold;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      background: #f7f7f7;
    }

    .a-header {
      color: #FFFF;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: left;
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans', sans-serif;
      /* Apply Phantom Sans font */
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .card {
      width: 350px;
      /* Adjusted to take half of the container width */
      height: 350px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 40px;
      box-shadow: 20px 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .text-content {
      width: 300px;
      /* Adjusted to take the other half of the container width */
      padding: 0 100px;
      /* Padding added for text content */
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-image: url('./img/bgimg.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

    .card-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .hoodie img {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ffff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans', sans-serif;
      /* Apply Phantom Sans font */

    }

    .requirement {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .c {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffff;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-family: 'Phantom Sans', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>

</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-container">
      <h1 class="a-header">
        Sprig
      </h1>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="hoodie">
          <img src="./img/sprig.png" alt="Hackathon Hoodie">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-content">
      <div class="description">
        <p>You got games on your phone? Well, I got games on my sprig. My little green buddy here isn't just for show â€“ it's my secret gaming oasis.</p>
        <p class="c">Achievement: Create your first sprig and submit it for the sprig grant.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>